reviewText: Absolutely everything I expected it to be!!!!!
Although I did enjoy this dvd, much of it does become repetitive. Very informative, w/ lots of close ups, but, as mentioned, very repetitive.
Love it Love it Love it!!!

dont waste your money. generic, home made piece of crap, edit horriable. the second disc is Stevie Nicks Through The Looking Glass that Amazon sells seperate !!! Shame on Amazon.
